{"tid":2200732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明生仔呢啲咁重要嘅嘢點解唔洗考牌","createTime":"2020-09-13T07:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T12:09:44.000Z","uid":370368,"like":22,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dbdcb08ea522b1e33206105f36fa1b87b087e144","tid":2200732,"uid":370368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"揸車要考牌，因為關乎性命安全<br />\n做專業人士要考牌，因為關乎操守<br />\n教琴要考牌，因為證明你合乎能力<br />\n咁點解生仔唔撚洗考牌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生個人出嚟以後係社會其中一份子<br />\n你點教佢就會有一個咩人出嚟<br />\n窮生仔都冇問題<br />\n你肯多啲陪佢心地好識教仔<br />\n個仔遲啲大個都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生個仔出嚟搞到個社會更加差嘅或者害咗一個人嘅<br />\n呢班廢柴父母真係自撚私<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話要解決事情癥結<br />\n生仔考牌咪解決囉<br />\n起碼都多好多保障先啦<br />\n開班教人點樣做個合格父母<br />\n考試pass左先俾佢生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果意外有咗<br />\n就強制性叫佢返呢啲course<br />\n唔好話麻煩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n養個仔成世仲撚麻煩你又諗住生？<br />\n一係帶返個套唔好玩中出囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f9b61fbda7e6946c1948fb2575d5bbc48c7693","tid":2200732,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />麻煩大家真係撳入去retweet 同 簽名聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p></strong></span></span><strong><span class=\"large\"><p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘥你幾分鐘時間 可以換手足生命安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢度有埋link 話你知12港人事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"h